Installation

All the dependencies must be fulfilled prior to installation. see website [ http://webuser.unicas.it/robbit/ ] for all the dependencies.

All the structures and classes are available in .h files, and the methods/functions are available in .c files.

To complie Robbit go to source directory and run: 
$> cmake . 

then 
$> make 

To execute run:
$> ./Robbit


Note: Configuration settings can be modified in the file "CMakeLists.txt" before starting the installation.
